{"word":"H1361 - גָּבַהּ - gâbahh - gaw-bah' - Exalt","slug":"H1361","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גָּבַהּ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gâbahh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gaw-bah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Exalt"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05D4;&#x05BC; - ga&#x0302;bahh</b> - <i>gaw-bah'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>soar</i>, that is, <i>be lofty</i>; figuratively to <i>be haughty: - </i>exalt, be haughty, be (make) high (-er), lift up, mount up, be proud, raise up great height, upward."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1362\">H1362</a>, <a href=\"#/H1363\">H1363</a>, <a href=\"#/H1364\">H1364</a>, <a href=\"#/H1365\">H1365</a>, <a href=\"#/H3011\">H3011</a>"}]}